	 in every price range but be advised it may sell out. We have very limited
	 seating available for guests on the day of the event so please make sure 
	you purchase accessible seating when you order tickets. Bags up to 12" x 6
	" x 12" are allowed in the venue. All bags will be searched prior to entry
	. For more FAQs please visit www.houston.houseofblues.com/faq\nBOX OFFICE:
